jQuery LightTip 1.0.1
Copyright 2010 Jonathan Wilsson
http://jonathanwilsson.com/projects/jquery-lighttip/

Requires at least jQuery 1.4.4.

LightTip is a jQuery plugin which allows you to create simple little tooltips on any element.

Look at the demo here: http://jonathanwilsson.com/projects/jquery-lighttip/

If you have any questions or thoughts feel free to contact me.

